# Lyyli.ai Brand Guidelines

## Värit / Colors
- Primary: Forest (#2F5D50)
- Secondary: Turquoise (#00B4D8)
- Accent: Rose (#FF6B6B)
- Neutral: Gray Light (#F8F9FA), Medium Gray (#6C757D), Dark Gray (#343A40)

## Typo
- Headings = Playfair Display, body = Inter (16px min)
- Kaikki otsikot: vain ensimmäisen sanan ensimmäinen kirjain isolla, muut pienellä

## Blog Post Formatting
- H2 headings (##) must use Playfair Display font for visual prominence
- Use double line breaks between major chapters/sections for better readability
- H3 subheadings (###) should be bold (**Subheading**) for clear hierarchy
- Remove horizontal lines (---) - use spacing instead
- Maintain consistent spacing and visual hierarchy throughout

## ICP Terminology
- English: Use "professional service company" or "professional service organization" instead of "expert team"
- Finnish: Use "asiantuntijaorganisaatio" instead of "asiantuntijatiimi"
- This applies to all copy, headings, descriptions, and marketing materials

## Sävy / Tone
- Professional but approachable
- Focus on business value and efficiency
- Avoid overly technical jargon
- Emphasize practical benefits

## Logo Usage
- Always maintain aspect ratio
- Minimum size: 120px width
- Use primary logo on light backgrounds
- Use white logo on dark backgrounds
